  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The shiny things in life were always too much to just ignore. Plus, they'd shine better with you. Years of petty theft has taught you how to do it correctly. You gain proficiency in Sleight of Hand or Security Kits. When you would make a check to pickpocket or pick a lock, You can mark the lock as your Primary Target, reducing the DC 2.</p><p>Doing this keeps the lock as your Target until you open it or an hour has passed.</p>",
